      "modified": "2026-03-15T11:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Operation FROZEN PIPELINE",
      "description": "Campagne d'intrusion multi-phases ciblant Europipe Energy Group via compromission initiale de la supply chain (NordValve Systems). Phase 1 : spearphishing sur NordValve. Phase 2 : mouvement latéral via tunnel VPN légitime vers réseau IT Europipe. Phase 3 : pivot IT-OT via jump server mal segmenté. Phase 4 : déploiement d'implant SCADA custom (GhostPLC). Phase 5 : exfiltration via DNS-over-HTTPS vers infrastructure C2.",
      "aliases": ["FROZENP", "NF-Campaign-2025-12"],
      "first_seen": "2025-09-15T00:00:00.000Z",
      "last_seen": "2026-02-28T00:00:00.000Z",
